$Id$

Alpha release of ``The Macro Implementation of SNOBOL4''
	(aka BTL SNOBOL4, MAINBOL) for Un*x.

This is a port of the original SIL (SNOBOL4 Implementation Language)
"macro" version of SNOBOL4 with the `C' language as a target.

****************************************************************

WARNING!!!  This is an VERY early release, for only the most die-hard!!

It is able to run it's own translation programs, but it has not been
thoughtly tested.  There is very little documentation!

If you make any changes/fixes/improvements, or port it to a new
system, please send me the diffs!

Phil Budne <budd@gnu.ai.mit.edu>

****************************************************************

See the file doc/GOALS for a description of the overall goals, and the
goals for this release.

See the file TODO for identified tasks / wish list.

